## Installation of GHC

Installation is based on [https://gist.github.com/yantonov/10083524](https://gist.github.com/yantonov/10083524)

    installghc X.Y.Z

where X.Y.Z  = release number (eg 8.8.1)

To use a GHC version, type

~~~
switchghc x.y.z
~~~

